data.description: Nestled in the award winning community of Meridiana- A 1.5 story four bedroom two bathroom home-1st floor has  living room dining room kitchen & 4 bedrooms-oversized game room/loft upstairs, home is perfect for those looking for extra space without the added cost of a full 2-story home-open floor plan-very spacious/comfortable-large living area, kitchen w/dining area-island-a breakfast bar-granite counter tops-Did I mention NO CARPET downstairs-oversized backyard w/covered patio great for entertaining-No back neighbors enjoy all the amenities such as the lazy river w/wave pool, pickle ball, disc golf, just to name a few-from daycare to high school your children never have to leave the subdivision-call today for your personal showing you will not be disappointed-home is move in ready
